description: Highly desirable but rarely available! Oversized three bedroom, two bath condo in the well-regarded Strawberry Hill Condominiums.  This duplex offers an open living space with hardwood floors throughout, a spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, with a breakfast bar and a separate dining area.  The first level also offers a generous sized primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and en-suite bath.  The lower level has two additional bedrooms and a newly renovated bathroom.  Central AC, in-unit laundry, private storage, and a deeded garage parking spot complete this offering. Conveniently located within proximity to both East and West side restaurants, grocery stores, coffee shops, & boutiques.
